sentences.english: It seemed as if the starlings had been hypnotised because they acted as if they were not being chased.
sentences.chinese: 椋鸟看似精神恍惚，因此它们的举动像没人追赶一样。

sentences.english: Emerald starlings are fairly small when compared with other such birds.
sentences.chinese: 与同类的其他鸟相比，翠辉椋鸟要小很多。

sentences.english: And starlings actually appear to be innocent in the case of the missing bluebirds.
sentences.chinese: 实际上，蓝知更鸟的数量减少和椋鸟并没有关系。

sentences.english: Oxpecker birds are found in large numbers where there are giraffes.
sentences.chinese: 在有长颈鹿的地方，总是能发现大量的牛椋鸟。

sentences.english: One of the main starling roosts is on top of the Town Hall.
sentences.chinese: 市政厅的房顶是星椋鸟的一个主要栖息处。
